{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.1","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 3:1","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.002.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.003.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-7: cf. Col 3:18, 19. 1 Ti 2:9-15. \u00c9p 5:22-23.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.3.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>\n    Femmes, soyez de m\u00eame soumises \u00e0 vos maris, afin que, si quelques-uns n\u2019ob\u00e9issent point \u00e0 la parole, ils soient gagn\u00e9s sans parole par la conduite de leurs femmes,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3","name":"1 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.2","name":"1 Pierre 3:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.25","name":"1 Pierre 2:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.2","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 3:2","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.003.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.003.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.3.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>en voyant votre mani\u00e8re de vivre chaste et r\u00e9serv\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3","name":"1 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.3","name":"1 Pierre 3:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.1","name":"1 Pierre 3:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.3","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 3:3","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.003.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.003.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.3.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Ayez, non cette parure ext\u00e9rieure qui consiste dans les cheveux tress\u00e9s, les ornements d\u2019or, ou les habits qu\u2019on rev\u00eat,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3","name":"1 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.4","name":"1 Pierre 3:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.2","name":"1 Pierre 3:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.4","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 3:4","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.003.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.003.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.3.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>mais la parure int\u00e9rieure et cach\u00e9e dans le c\u0153ur, la puret\u00e9 incorruptible d\u2019un esprit doux et paisible, qui est d\u2019un grand prix devant Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3","name":"1 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.5","name":"1 Pierre 3:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.3","name":"1 Pierre 3:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.5","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 3:5","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.003.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.003.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.3.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Ainsi se paraient autrefois les saintes femmes qui esp\u00e9raient en Dieu, soumises \u00e0 leurs maris,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3","name":"1 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.6","name":"1 Pierre 3:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.4","name":"1 Pierre 3:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.6","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 3:6","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.003.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.003.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.3.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>comme Sara, qui ob\u00e9issait \u00e0 Abraham et l\u2019appelait son seigneur. C\u2019est d\u2019elle que vous \u00eates devenues les filles, en faisant ce qui est bien, sans vous laisser troubler par aucune crainte.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3","name":"1 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.7","name":"1 Pierre 3:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.5","name":"1 Pierre 3:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.7","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 3:7","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.003.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.003.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.3.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Maris, montrez \u00e0 votre tour de la sagesse dans vos rapports avec vos femmes, comme avec un sexe plus faible; honorez-les, comme devant aussi h\u00e9riter avec vous de la gr\u00e2ce de la vie. Qu\u2019il en soit ainsi, afin que rien ne vienne faire obstacle \u00e0 vos pri\u00e8res.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3","name":"1 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.8","name":"1 Pierre 3:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.6","name":"1 Pierre 3:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.8","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 3:8","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.003.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.003.009,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 8-17: cf. (Ro 12:14-21. Ps 34:13-18.) (Mt 10:24-31. 1 Pi 2:12, 19, 20.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.3.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Enfin, soyez tous anim\u00e9s des m\u00eames pens\u00e9es et des m\u00eames sentiments, pleins d\u2019amour fraternel, de compassion, d\u2019humilit\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3","name":"1 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.9","name":"1 Pierre 3:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.7","name":"1 Pierre 3:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.9","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 3:9","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.003.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.003.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.3.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Ne rendez point mal pour mal, ou injure pour injure; b\u00e9nissez, au contraire, car c\u2019est \u00e0 cela que vous avez \u00e9t\u00e9 appel\u00e9s, afin d\u2019h\u00e9riter la b\u00e9n\u00e9diction.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3","name":"1 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.10","name":"1 Pierre 3:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.8","name":"1 Pierre 3:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.10","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 3:10","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.003.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.003.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"1Pet.3.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>\n    Si quelqu\u2019un, en effet, veut aimer la vie<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et voir des jours heureux,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Qu\u2019il pr\u00e9serve sa langue du mal<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et ses l\u00e8vres des paroles trompeuses,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3","name":"1 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.11","name":"1 Pierre 3:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.9","name":"1 Pierre 3:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.11","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 3:11","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.003.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.003.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"1Pet.3.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>\n    Qu\u2019il s\u2019\u00e9loigne du mal et fasse le bien,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Qu\u2019il recherche la paix et la poursuive;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3","name":"1 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.12","name":"1 Pierre 3:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.10","name":"1 Pierre 3:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.12","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 3:12","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.003.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.003.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"1Pet.3.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Car les yeux du Seigneur sont sur les justes<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et ses oreilles sont attentives \u00e0 leur pri\u00e8re,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mais la face du Seigneur est contre ceux qui font le mal.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3","name":"1 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.13","name":"1 Pierre 3:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.11","name":"1 Pierre 3:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.13","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 3:13","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.003.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.003.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.3.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Et qui vous maltraitera, si vous \u00eates z\u00e9l\u00e9s pour le bien?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3","name":"1 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.14","name":"1 Pierre 3:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.12","name":"1 Pierre 3:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.14","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 3:14","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.003.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.003.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.3.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>D\u2019ailleurs, quand vous souffririez pour la justice, vous seriez heureux. N\u2019ayez d\u2019eux aucune crainte, et ne soyez pas troubl\u00e9s;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3","name":"1 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.15","name":"1 Pierre 3:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.13","name":"1 Pierre 3:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.15","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 3:15","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.003.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.003.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.3.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Mais sanctifiez dans vos c\u0153urs Christ le Seigneur, \u00e9tant toujours pr\u00eats \u00e0 vous d\u00e9fendre, avec douceur et respect, devant quiconque vous demande raison de l\u2019esp\u00e9rance qui est en vous,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3","name":"1 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.16","name":"1 Pierre 3:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.14","name":"1 Pierre 3:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.16","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 3:16","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.003.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.003.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.3.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>et ayant une bonne conscience, afin que, l\u00e0 m\u00eame o\u00f9 ils vous calomnient comme si vous \u00e9tiez des malfaiteurs, ceux qui d\u00e9crient votre bonne conduite en Christ soient couverts de confusion.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3","name":"1 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.17","name":"1 Pierre 3:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.15","name":"1 Pierre 3:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.17","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 3:17","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.003.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.003.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.3.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Car il vaut mieux souffrir, si telle est la volont\u00e9 de Dieu, en faisant le bien qu\u2019en faisant le mal.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3","name":"1 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.18","name":"1 Pierre 3:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.16","name":"1 Pierre 3:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.18","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 3:18","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.003.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.003.019,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Exemple de J\u00e9sus-Christ, qui a souffert pour nous: conduite \u00e0 tenir; consolations \u00e0 esp\u00e9rer<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 18-22: cf. 1 Pi 2:21-24. (H\u00e9 11:7. Ro 6:3, 4; 10:9, 10.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.3.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>\n    Christ aussi a souffert une fois pour les p\u00e9ch\u00e9s, lui juste pour des injustes, afin de nous amener \u00e0 Dieu, ayant \u00e9t\u00e9 mis \u00e0 mort quant \u00e0 la chair, mais ayant \u00e9t\u00e9 rendu vivant quant \u00e0 l\u2019Esprit,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3","name":"1 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.19","name":"1 Pierre 3:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.17","name":"1 Pierre 3:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.19","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 3:19","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.003.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.003.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.3.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>dans lequel aussi il est all\u00e9 pr\u00eacher aux esprits en prison,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3","name":"1 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.20","name":"1 Pierre 3:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.18","name":"1 Pierre 3:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.20","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 3:20","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.003.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.003.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.3.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>qui autrefois avaient \u00e9t\u00e9 incr\u00e9dules, lorsque la patience de Dieu se prolongeait, aux jours de No\u00e9, pendant la construction de l\u2019arche, dans laquelle un petit nombre de personnes, c\u2019est-\u00e0-dire, huit, furent sauv\u00e9es \u00e0 travers l\u2019eau.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3","name":"1 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.21","name":"1 Pierre 3:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.19","name":"1 Pierre 3:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.21","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 3:21","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.003.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.003.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.3.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Cette eau \u00e9tait une figure du bapt\u00eame, qui n\u2019est pas la purification des souillures du corps, mais l\u2019engagement d\u2019une bonne conscience envers Dieu, et qui maintenant vous sauve, vous aussi, par la r\u00e9surrection de J\u00e9sus-Christ,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3","name":"1 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.22","name":"1 Pierre 3:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.20","name":"1 Pierre 3:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.22","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 3:22","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.003.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.004.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.3.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>qui est \u00e0 la droite de Dieu, depuis qu\u2019il est all\u00e9 au ciel, et que les anges, les autorit\u00e9s et les puissances, lui ont \u00e9t\u00e9 soumis.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3","name":"1 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.1","name":"1 Pierre 4:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.21","name":"1 Pierre 3:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fbfdf5229.89455969');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbfdf5229.89455969\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fbfdf5229.89455969","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fbfdf5229.89455969'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbfdf5229.89455969\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}